title: Zauber von OS
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An alternative bar that offers some veggie food and occasionally a vegan cake. Try the vöner (seitan-döner with house-made seitan). Seitan patties, when available, can be used to make a burger. Kitchen is flexible in terms of food preparation. Hosts live music.
